description:
Every time a new row is added to your Google Sheets spreadsheet, Make will automatically create an event Ticket with a QR code and dynamic data. The template uses this [example spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1TT20-T21gBQkIfJ3zG7fDB6lgT-KRd3OLus4rgzxhA0/edit?usp=sharing
) and this [example ticket](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1yjUsldnKD0VT1o1igfY8Y-SLWT2J9M3VG4t4Wb5ibKw/edit?usp=sharing
).
